flowchart TD
    SP[SharePoint Online<br/>System of record<br/>Original files remain here]
    ING[Azure Function<br/>Submission discovery<br/>Metadata scan only]
    SB[Azure Service Bus<br/>Primary workload buffer<br/>Absorbs bursts]
    ORCH[Durable Functions Orchestrator<br/>One workflow per submission]
    YAML[Yaml Definitions<br/>Known form types<br/>Known attachment types<br/>Validation rules]
    OCR[Azure Document Intelligence<br/>OCR and text extraction]
    ROUTE[YAML-aware Routing<br/>Classify form and attachments<br/>against known types]
    VAL[Generic Validation Engine<br/>Apply YAML rules]
    AI[Azure OpenAI / Foundry Models<br/>Structured extraction<br/>Soft judgment]
    PY[Deterministic Python<br/>Date logic<br/>Required docs<br/>Exact rule enforcement]
    BLOB[Azure Blob Storage<br/>Durable runtime state<br/>Optional audit artifacts<br/>Optional YAML storage]
    OUT[SharePoint Results<br/>CSV by form type]
    SCALE[Future scale-out pattern<br/>Optional OCR / LLM / validation queues]

    SP -->|Discover files| ING
    ING -->|Submission manifest| SB
    SB -->|Queued submission| ORCH
    ORCH --> YAML
    ORCH -->|Fetch files on demand| SP
    ORCH --> OCR
    OCR --> ROUTE
    YAML --> ROUTE
    ROUTE --> VAL
    VAL --> AI
    AI --> VAL
    VAL --> PY
    PY --> VAL
    VAL --> ORCH
    ORCH --> OUT
    ORCH --> BLOB
    ORCH -.-> SCALE
